<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA60">
<l>pērntoṉṟu nōkkātu piṉṉiṟpāy nillāppā</l>
<l>yīṉtuḻāy māyaṉaiyē yeṉṉeñcē pērnteṅkun</l>
<l>tollaimā vennarakiṟ cērāmal kāppataṟ</l>
<l>killaikāṇ maṟṟō riṟai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come back, don’t look at anything, stand behind the Dark one with</l>
<l>productive Tulsi [or] rush forth without standing, my heart. Turning anywhere,</l>
<l>for protecting [us] from joining the old big hot hell</l>
<l>there is no other lord, see.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
